data.description: This beautiful 2-story home boasts an abundance of natural light that fills every corner, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere!   As you step inside, you're immediately captivated by the breathtaking Pike Peak views that grace the living spaces.  The heart of the home is the open kitchen, a chef's dream, featuring a large island with ample seating, granite countertops, and sleek stainless steel appliances. This kitchen is perfect for culinary adventures and entertaining, as it seamlessly connects to the dining and living areas.   Beautiful iron railings lead you upstairs to four of the 6 bedrooms.   The spacious primary bedroom offers a true retreat with double closets providing ample storage space. The attached en-suite bathroom is a luxurious haven with a large soaking tub, a separate tiled shower and a large window perfectly framing Pikes Peak.     Three additional spacious bedrooms, the laundry room & full bathroom complete the bright and airy second floor.     Heading to the basement, you’ll find a large recreation area perfect for a second living room, exercise space, play room etc!  Two additional bedrooms and a bathroom are tucked in the back of the basement for optimal privacy.     The backyard is full fenced and backs to open space with no back neighbors. Enjoy the mountain views under the covered back patio.     This home offers all the space, storage and style all in a convenient location!
